      <title>If compliments make you feel super awkward, this comic is for you</title>
      <author>Andee Tagle</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/08/02/nx-s1-5442506/hard-to-accept-compliments-comic</link>
      <comments>https://text.npr.org/2025/08/02/nx-s1-5442506/hard-to-accept-compliments-comic</comments>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.npr.org/2025/08/02/nx-s1-5442506/hard-to-accept-compliments-comic</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 02 Aug 2025 09:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;div id="storytext" class="storytext storylocation linkLocation"&gt;       &lt;p&gt;Love your outfit! Great presentation! Cool glasses! When someone praises you, do you accept it? Or dismiss it? &lt;/p&gt;   &lt;p&gt;Your reaction says a lot about how you feel about yourself, and it can affect how the other person feels too, say researchers. &lt;/p&gt;   &lt;p&gt;Social psychologist &lt;a href="https://www.ericaboothby.com/" target="_blank"&gt;Erica Boothby&lt;/a&gt; and behavioral scientist &lt;a href="https://www.xuan-zhao.com/" target="_blank"&gt;Xuan Zhao&lt;/a&gt; explain the science of compliments — and make the case for accepting someone's kind remarks about you. &lt;/p&gt;   &lt;div id="resg-s1-80629" class="bucketwrap image large"&gt;             &lt;div     class="imagewrap has-source-dimensions"     data-crop-type=""     style="         --source-width: 2500;         --source-height: 3125;     " &gt;         &lt;picture&gt;             &lt;source srcset="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/2500x3125+0+0/resize/400/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F6f%2F9b%2F56428e704ffca773fa72ee7ab43f%2Fcompliments-1.jpg 400w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/2500x3125+0+0/resize/600/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F6f%2F9b%2F56428e704ffca773fa72ee7ab43f%2Fcompliments-1.jpg 600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/2500x3125+0+0/resize/800/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F6f%2F9b%2F56428e704ffca773fa72ee7ab43f%2Fcompliments-1.jpg 800w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/2500x3125+0+0/resize/900/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F6f%2F9b%2F56428e704ffca773fa72ee7ab43f%2Fcompliments-1.jpg 900w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/2500x3125+0+0/resize/1200/quality/